name: INDIFFERENCE SILVER EARRINGS
description:
WALK FOR GOLD's fourth edition is inspired by people's actions, about moral courage and to be everything but indifferent. The theme INDIFFERENCE is made to set off a developing process. The pieces are designed in simplicity like simple actions that everyone can make. 

The earrings in silver with oxidated parts is made stylistically pure and with a simple twist in function. The combination makes them a dashing appearance to the ear in ordinary action.

name: INDIFFERENCE SILVER CHAIN
description: WALK FOR GOLD's fourth edition is inspired by people's actions, about moral courage and to be everything but indifferent. The theme INDIFFERENCE is made to set off a developing process. The pieces are designed in simplicity like simple actions that everyone can make. First out is the unisex silver chain that is partly oxidated. It is a jewellery that is suitable for all occasions in your everyday life.

name: NOT FOR SALE PENDANT
description:
WALK FOR GOLD’s third collection, NOT FOR SALE, makes a strong statement against trafficking. The shape has been developed as a symbol of the freedom we all got the right to. That’s why the design has taken the shape of swallows that flies freely. With this collection, WALK FOR GOLD will put money into organisations for victims of trafficking.

The Swallow necklace brings the silver swallows right to your heart. It is made in a pair of two birds, placed in a unique way combined with a chain in silver.

name: DICE EARRINGS small
description:
WALK FOR GOLD's second collection DICE is established from gambling and gambling disorders which are a current subject in today's every-day-life. We first launched this collection in October 2009 at the Stockholm Technical Fair in Sweden.

DICE small earring shows with its blank surface the emptiness which unhealthy gambling can cause. 

Material: 925 Silver 
Weight: 2 g

name: DICE PENDANT
description:
WALK FOR GOLD's second collection DICE is established from gambling and gambling disorders which are a current subject in today's every-day-life. We first launched this collection in October 2009 at the Stockholm Technical Fair in Sweden.
You can change the game in life with an action by yourself no matter what your luck is about. 

This DICE pendant symbolizes a change of bad luck. The choice is yours to choose your lucky colour on the 36 stones. With this you will simply have your luck around your neck.
For more information about colours, please contact WALK FOR GOLD at contact@walkforgold.com

Material: 925 Silver 
Chain: 70 cm (possible to get in different lengths)

name: DIAMOND SILVER BRACELET
description:
WALK FOR GOLD's first launch is the DIAMOND collection of bracelets that is inspired by the fight against Blood Diamonds. We make a strong revulsion of the conflict diamonds.

The silver bracelet is a “diamond” you will wear with good conscience. A fairly made jewellery that is elementary product in this collection.

Material: 925 Silver
